title: Law Of Reincarnation
description: A second chance to get with an old first love, the main character travels 3 years back in time to his first year at the company. But his efforts to get closer to her don’t work and a sunbae who was very serious and professional starts to seduce him… “It’s embarrassing if I’m the only one who strips… Hurry up and take it off. Unless you want me to do it for you?”
author: Matgini & Naru
